01:37.097 --> 01:40.970
♪ [I'LL BE READY]

01:41.101 --> 01:43.755
♪ FOREVER AND ALWAYS

01:43.886 --> 01:46.932
♪ I'M ALWAYS HERE.

02:03.297 --> 02:04.863
♪ IT'S SUMMERTIME

02:05.603 --> 02:08.389
♪ BUT NOBODY SEEMS
TO BE TAKING IT EASY ♪

