♪ IF I NEVER TALK TO YOU

02:48.777 --> 02:50.692
♪ MEMORIES ARE ALWAYS SHARED

02:50.822 --> 02:52.868
♪ YOU BECOME A MYSTERY

02:52.998 --> 02:55.000
♪ TIME BECOMES OUR ENEMY

02:55.131 --> 02:57.089
♪ I JUST WANT YOU
HERE WITH ME ♪

02:57.220 --> 03:00.702
♪ AND I'M TELLING
YOU IT'S HIGH TIME. ♪

03:25.117 --> 03:27.381
-CODY: HEY, READY
FOR THAT CPR CLASS?

03:27.511 --> 03:31.298
-HUH? YEAH. TAKE
A LOOK AT THAT.

03:31.428 --> 03:32.516
-CODY: WHAT?

03:33.169 --> 03:34.649
-NEELY: DON'T YOU SEE IT?

03:34.779 --> 03:36.607
-CODY: MITCH AND
SAM WASHING A TRUCK?

03:37.217 --> 03:39.958
-NO, LOOK AT THE WAY THEY'RE
LOOKING AT ONE ANOTHER.

03:40.089 --> 03:42.352
-CODY: WHAT? THEY'RE SMILING,
SO WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?

03:42.483 --> 03:44.572
-THEY'RE IN LOVE, CODY.

03:44.702 --> 03:46.443
-MITCH AND SAM? [CHUCKLES]

03:46.922 --> 03:49.141
NOT A CHANCE.
-THEY'RE IN LOVE.

03:49.272 --> 03:50.969
-OH, THEY'RE
FRIENDS, THAT'S ALL.

03:51.927 --> 03:53.407
-IT'S CHANGED, TRUST ME.

03:53.537 --> 03:55.104
BODY LANGUAGE DOESN'T LIE.

03:55.235 --> 03:57.411
I MEAN, LOOK AT THE WAY
HIS HIPS ARE THRUST FORWARD

03:57.541 --> 03:58.760
AND HIS LEGS ARE
SLIGHTLY SPREAD.

04:00.152 --> 04:02.851
YOU SEE? SHE JUST
CARESSED HIS ARM.

04:02.981 --> 04:05.201
-SHE ACCIDENTALLY
TOUCHED HIM, NEELY.

04:05.332 --> 04:06.724
-THAT'S NO ACCIDENT.

04:06.855 --> 04:09.205
I CAN SMELL THE HORMONES
ALL THE WAY UP HERE.

04:09.727 --> 04:11.599
-YOU KNOW, YOU SHOULD
GET A 900-NUMBER.

04:11.729 --> 04:14.776
THE NEELY CAPSHAW
PSYCHIC LOVE LINE.

04:16.343 --> 04:17.995
COME ON, LET'S GO.
NEWMIE'S WAITING.

04:20.434 --> 04:22.349
-MITCH: HEY, HEY.
WHOA, LOOK OUT!

04:22.479 --> 04:23.872
THERE'S A SPOT, THERE'S
A SPOT RIGHT THERE!

04:24.002 --> 04:26.091
[LAUGHING]

04:37.277 --> 04:39.453
-MY LINE OF WORK, ESE.

04:39.583 --> 04:41.716
[SERIOUS GUITAR MUSIC]

04:59.342 --> 05:01.083
WHAT YOU LOOKING AT, ESE?

05:02.084 --> 05:04.913
-BLUE TRUNKS. HE'S RIVERSIDE.

05:05.043 --> 05:06.393
USED TO BE MY HOMEBOY.

05:06.523 --> 05:07.698
-YOUR HOMEBOY?

05:08.308 --> 05:09.483
LOOKS MORE LIKE A BEACH BOY.

05:09.613 --> 05:10.571
[LAUGHING]

05:10.701 --> 05:11.876
-QUIT TALKING, GET TO WORK.

05:20.102 --> 05:22.452
-YOU'RE GONNA HAVE YOUR
WORK CUT FOR YOU TODAY WITH THESE GUYS.

05:23.932 --> 05:25.020
YEAH.

05:27.022 --> 05:29.241
-HEY, HOW, MANY ARE
TAKING THE CPR CLASS?

05:29.372 --> 05:30.242
-FIFTEEN.

05:31.374 --> 05:33.028
-MANNY, WE'RE GONNA USE
YOU AS A VICTIM, HON.

05:33.158 --> 05:34.334
-AW, MAN.

05:34.464 --> 05:36.074
BOY, I HOPE AT
LEAST GONNA WASH UP

05:36.205 --> 05:37.772
AFTER PICKING UP THAT TRASH.

05:38.425 --> 05:40.340
-NOT LIKELY.
-HEY, QUIT COMPLAINING.

05:40.470 --> 05:42.777
MAKING THEM LEARN CPR IS A PART
OF THEIR COMMUNITY SERVICE.

05:42.907 --> 05:44.387
IT'S A GREAT IDEA.

05:44.518 --> 05:46.258
-YEAH, THEY TAG WALLS
AND VANDALIZE STORES,

05:46.389 --> 05:47.477
AND WE GET THE PUNISHMENT.

05:48.478 --> 05:51.307
-LOOK, I'M SURE MOST OF
THEM ARE PRETTY GOOD KIDS,

05:51.438 --> 05:53.396
JUST GOT INTO SOME TROUBLE.

06:01.186 --> 06:02.710
-HEY, CHULA.

06:03.232 --> 06:04.929
HEY, YOU BETTER WATCH WHERE
YOU'RE GOING, EIGHTBALL!

06:07.018 --> 06:09.673
-I'M SORRY, PEPE.
I DIDN'T SEE YOU.

06:10.674 --> 06:12.850
-SORRY TOO, ESE,
I DIDN'T SEE YOU EITHER.

06:14.896 --> 06:15.723
-YO, MAN, WHAT'S UP?

06:15.853 --> 06:16.898
[GRUNTING]

06:19.857 --> 06:22.251
[SERIOUS MUSIC]

06:30.520 --> 06:31.826
-HEY, CUT IT OUT!

06:44.926 --> 06:47.015
-CODY: THEY'RE KIDS, RIGHT?
-NEWMIE: YEAH.

06:47.145 --> 06:49.583
-STAY HERE, MAKE SURE
EVERYTHING'S OKAY, ALRIGHT?

06:53.282 --> 06:54.762
-CODY: HEY, BREAK IT UP!

06:54.892 --> 06:56.981
[GRUNTING AND RABBLING]

06:59.070 --> 07:01.246
-I'M CALLING THE COPS.
-LET'S GO, HUH?

07:01.377 --> 07:04.119
-ESE! LET'S END IT
NOW, CHANGO, LET'S GO!

07:04.249 --> 07:06.643
-YOU WANT SOME OF
ME? MAN, WHAT'S UP!

07:06.774 --> 07:09.516
-HECTOR.
-HEY, HOLMES. BEEN A LONG TIME.

07:09.646 --> 07:10.952
-YOU WANT THEM
TO CALL THE COPS?

07:11.082 --> 07:12.606
YOU WANT TO BOTH
TO END UP IN JAIL?

07:12.736 --> 07:14.434
-MAN, HE STUCK ME, MAN!
MAN, WHAT'S UP WITH THAT?

07:14.564 --> 07:16.348
-IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.
-WANNA GET DOWN, PUNK?

07:16.479 --> 07:18.089
I'M GONNA PUNCH YOU
IN THE FACE!

07:18.220 --> 07:19.439
-QUIET DOWN!

07:21.658 --> 07:23.617
-YOU KNOW WHAT, CHANGO!
YOU'RE GOING DOWN, ESE!

07:23.747 --> 07:25.227
-LET'S GO!

07:25.357 --> 07:27.185
-CABRONE, YOU
AIN'T NOTHIN', ESE!

07:27.316 --> 07:30.101
-TAKE HIM, THROW HIM IN
THE WATER IF YOU HAVE TO.

07:30.798 --> 07:32.190
ANY MORE "ACCIDENTS"

07:32.321 --> 07:33.670
AND IT'LL BE THE COPS
DRAGGING YOU AWAY.

07:33.801 --> 07:35.106
NEXT TIME, YOU'RE
GONNA DO TIME, BUDDY.

07:35.237 --> 07:36.630
AND GET OUT OF HERE!

07:36.760 --> 07:39.720
-PULGA: OKAY, BARBIE
DOLL. [DEVIOUS SNICKER]

07:40.372 --> 07:42.636
-NOW, I THINK THEY'RE READY
TO LEARN HOW TO SAVE LIVES

07:42.766 --> 07:44.115
INSTEAD OF WASTE SOME, OKAY.

07:44.942 --> 07:46.944
-ALL RIGHT.
EVERYBODY ON THE BEACH.

07:47.075 --> 07:48.206
-ALL RIGHT.

07:49.294 --> 07:50.992
-MAN, WHY YOU'RE
HERE, MAN, WHAT YOU DO?

07:51.775 --> 07:52.863
-WHY AM I HERE?

07:53.429 --> 07:54.778
WHY ARE YOU HERE, HOLMES?

07:54.909 --> 07:56.867
-I'M DOING SOMETHING
WITH MY LIFE, MAN.

07:56.998 --> 07:58.086
I WANNA BE A LIFEGUARD.

07:58.695 --> 08:00.262
-YEAH, YOU BETTER
BE A LIFEGUARD,

08:00.392 --> 08:01.959
IF YOU EVER COME
BACK TO THE BARRIO.

08:08.400 --> 08:09.445
-NEWMIE: ALL RIGHT,
FIND YOUR PARTNERS

08:09.576 --> 08:11.099
AND SETTLE DOWN, LET'S GO.

08:16.234 --> 08:19.673
-NEELY: ALL RIGHT,
EVERYONE, PAY ATTENTION.

08:20.238 --> 08:22.980
HI, MY NAME IS NEELY CAPSHAW
AND THIS IS CODY MADISON.

08:23.111 --> 08:25.548
WE'RE HERE TO TEACH
YOU HOW TO SAVE A LIFE.

08:26.114 --> 08:28.159
-ALL RIGHT, I WANT ALL THE
VICTIMS ON THE BLUE TOWELS

08:28.290 --> 08:29.247
TO LIE FLAT ON YOUR BACK.

08:30.335 --> 08:32.294
NOW THE RESCUER, YOU'RE
GONNA FIND THE HOLLOW AREA

08:32.424 --> 08:35.078
UNDER THE RIB CAGE OF
YOUR PARTNER'S CHEST.

08:35.210 --> 08:37.255
[GIGGLING]
-CODY: FIND THE HOLLOW AREA.

08:37.385 --> 08:38.822
-I'M TICKLISH, HOLMES.

08:38.953 --> 08:41.042
-NOW MEASURE UP THREE
FINGERS FROM THERE,

08:41.172 --> 08:42.565
PUT YOUR HAND ABOVE IT,

08:42.696 --> 08:44.567
AND YOUR OTHER HAND
ON TOP OF THAT ONE.

08:45.612 --> 08:48.049
NOW FEEL YOUR PARTNER'S
HEART BEATING.

08:48.179 --> 08:50.399
-REALLY FEEL IT, EACH BEAT.

08:50.530 --> 08:52.053
PICTURE BLOOD
PUMPING THROUGH IT.

08:52.183 --> 08:54.577
-OH, YEAH, I FEEL IT.
-THROUGH THE ENTIRE BODY.

08:55.360 --> 08:57.275
-NOW PUT YOUR
HANDS IN THE SAND.

08:57.406 --> 08:58.929
WHAT DO YOU FEEL?

09:00.191 --> 09:02.716
-SAND.
-ALUMINUM.

09:02.846 --> 09:03.978
WHAT KIND OF TRASH
BEACH IS THIS?

09:04.108 --> 09:06.589
[LAUGHING]

09:06.720 --> 09:07.764
-THE KIND YOU'RE
HERE TO CLEAN UP.

09:07.895 --> 09:10.550
[LAUGHING AND HOOTING]

09:11.115 --> 09:13.683
-WHAT YOU FEEL IS
THE ABSENCE OF LIFE.

09:13.814 --> 09:16.338
NO MATTER WHAT YOU DO,
YOU CAN'T BREATHE LIFE

09:16.468 --> 09:17.992
OR PUMP LIFE INTO THE SAND.

09:18.122 --> 09:21.169
BUT YOU CAN BREATHE
LIFE AND PUMP LIFE

09:21.299 --> 09:23.606
INTO ANOTHER HUMAN
BEING WHO IS DYING

09:23.737 --> 09:25.042
OR ARE ALREADY DEAD.

09:25.173 --> 09:27.523
YOU GUYS CAN BRING
HIM BACK TO LIFE.

09:28.176 --> 09:30.221
YOU HOLD THAT POWER
IN YOUR HANDS.

09:32.441 --> 09:34.661
-ALL RIGHT, PUT YOUR HANDS
BACK ON YOUR PARTNER'S CHEST,

09:34.791 --> 09:37.881
FIND THE SPOT, THREE
FINGERS UP, LET'S GO.

09:38.012 --> 09:40.188
-CPR CAN SAVE
A PERSON'S LIFE.

09:40.318 --> 09:43.321
THE ODDS ARE IT'S GONNA BE
A RELATIVE OR A LOVED ONE.

09:43.452 --> 09:44.758
LEARN IT.

09:44.888 --> 09:46.237
IF YOU EVER FEEL
LIKE TAKING A LIFE,

09:47.151 --> 09:48.370
MAYBE YOU'LL HAVE
SECOND THOUGHTS.

09:50.720 --> 09:52.417
-HEY, ARE YOU LISTENING?

09:53.114 --> 09:54.594
-THE JUDGE SAID
I GOTTA BE HERE.

09:54.724 --> 09:56.160
DIDN'T SAY
I GOTTA LISTEN, FOOL.

09:56.291 --> 09:57.814
-SMART.

09:57.945 --> 09:59.860
-WELL, I SAY YOU GOTTA
LISTEN, SO PAY ATTENTION.

10:00.425 --> 10:03.994
-ALL RIGHT, ALL YOU
HAVE TO REMEMBER IS ABC.

10:04.125 --> 10:07.128
AIRWAY,
BREATHING, CIRCULATION.

10:07.258 --> 10:10.000
THE FIRST THING YOU DO,
IS CLEAR THE AIRWAY.

10:10.653 --> 10:13.308
TILT THE HEAD BACK,
LIFT THE CHIN.

10:14.352 --> 10:16.964
-DO IT, NOW.
ON YOUR PARTNER.

10:20.358 --> 10:22.578
-NOW, LOOK, LISTEN AND FEEL.

10:22.709 --> 10:24.798
PLACE YOUR EAR NEAR TO
YOUR PARTNER'S OPEN MOUTH,

10:24.928 --> 10:26.364
AND LOOK AT THEIR CHEST.

10:26.495 --> 10:27.844
-I RATHER LOOK AT YOUR
CHEST, BARBIE DOLL.

10:28.889 --> 10:29.672
IN YOUR PINK CORVETTE.

10:29.803 --> 10:31.500
-HEY, THAT'S ENOUGH.

10:31.631 --> 10:33.589
-ANYONE WHO FAILS THIS
COURSE WON'T GET CREDIT

10:33.720 --> 10:36.070
FOR ANYTHING TODAY,
SO YOU BETTER KNOW WHAT TO DO.

10:36.200 --> 10:38.115
-ALL RIGHT, NOW, YOU HAVE TO
LOOK AT YOUR PARTNER'S CHEST

10:38.246 --> 10:39.639
TO RISE AND FALL.

10:39.769 --> 10:41.466
AND LISTEN AND FEEL
FOR BREATH, ALRIGHT?

10:42.859 --> 10:45.514
IF THEY'RE NOT BREATHING,
GIVE TWO VENTILATIONS.

10:45.645 --> 10:48.430
KEEP THE HEAD TILTED BACK,
PINCH YOUR PARTNER'S NOSE,

10:48.560 --> 10:51.215
PLACE YOUR MOUTH OVER
HIS AND BLOW TWICE.

10:52.521 --> 10:54.175
-NOW, DO IT.

10:54.305 --> 10:55.829
-KISS ME AND YOU DIE, ESE.

10:55.959 --> 10:58.135
[LAUGHING]

10:58.266 --> 11:00.268
-HEY, HEY, HEY, ALRIGHT,
ALRIGHT. THAT'S IT.

11:00.398 --> 11:01.835
HEY, WE'RE GONNA SWITCH.

11:02.487 --> 11:04.228
YOU'RE GONNA GO OVER HERE.

11:04.359 --> 11:05.752
YOU, OVER HERE.

11:05.882 --> 11:07.623
-HEY, ANYONE BUT HIM.
-HEY, GET OVER IT.

11:07.754 --> 11:09.364
YOU, OVER TO THIS SIDE.

11:09.494 --> 11:10.234
-I AIN'T GOING OVER THERE.

11:10.365 --> 11:11.192
-YES, YOU ARE.

11:11.845 --> 11:13.020
-GET OFF ME, MAN.

11:13.150 --> 11:14.848
-ON YOUR KNEES,
RIGHT HERE. GO ON.

11:14.978 --> 11:16.240
-NO WAY, MAN. AIN'T NO WAY--

11:16.371 --> 11:17.677
-NEWMIE: SHUT UP.

11:17.807 --> 11:20.157
HEY, IT'S THIS OR
JAIL TIME, BUDDY.

11:20.288 --> 11:22.072
-LOOK, YOU GUYS,
THIS ISN'T KISSING.

11:22.203 --> 11:23.857
THIS IS BREATHING
AIR INTO EMPTY LUNGS.

11:23.987 --> 11:25.336
NOW TWO VENTILATIONS, LET'S GO.

11:25.467 --> 11:26.686
-DO IT!

11:26.816 --> 11:28.513
-NOW.

11:29.819 --> 11:31.647
-HECTOR, COME ON
MAN, JUST TRY IT.

11:32.517 --> 11:34.781
PINCH MY NOSE AND
INFLATE MY LUNGS.

11:35.912 --> 11:37.522
-YOU BETTER WATCH IT, SMOKE.

11:37.653 --> 11:39.481
-I HATE THIS AS MUCH AS YOU.

11:39.960 --> 11:41.004
MORE THAN YOU.

11:44.486 --> 11:45.748
[GAGGING]

11:45.879 --> 11:47.619
-THIS GUY'S GOT
BAD BREATH, HOLMES!

11:47.750 --> 11:48.708
-YOU SON OF A--!

11:49.796 --> 11:50.971
-DON'T LET HIM
BAIT YOU. COOL IT!

11:51.101 --> 11:52.712
-GET OFF ME, MAN.

11:52.842 --> 11:54.278
-DO IT.

11:54.409 --> 11:56.106
-DOG BREATH, HOLMES.

11:57.412 --> 11:59.719
-HEY! CAN WE CONTINUE NOW?

12:01.285 --> 12:03.766
NOW NEXT, WE'RE GONNA
CHECK THE VICTIM'S PULSE.

12:03.897 --> 12:05.637
YOU'LL DO THAT BY
PLACING YOUR FINGERS

12:05.768 --> 12:07.248
ON THE CAROTID
ARTERY IN THE NECK.

12:08.336 --> 12:11.295
-IF THERE'S NO BREATH
OR PULSE, YOU BEGIN CPR.

12:11.426 --> 12:13.602
IF YOU'RE ALONE,
YOU DO 15 AND TWO.

12:13.733 --> 12:17.432
15 CHEST COMPRESSIONS,
THEN TWO VENTILATIONS.

12:17.562 --> 12:19.826
-ONCE YOU START
CPR, YOU NEVER STOP.

12:19.956 --> 12:21.653
NEVER STOP UNTIL
SECOND AID ARRIVES.

12:21.784 --> 12:23.525
YOU'RE FIRST AID.

12:23.655 --> 12:25.527
YOU KEEP GOING UNTIL A MORE
QUALIFIED PERSON GETS THERE

12:25.657 --> 12:28.399
SUCH AS A PARAMEDIC, OR
A LIFEGUARD, ALRIGHT?

12:29.052 --> 12:31.533
-ALL RIGHT, FIND A
SPOT, THREE FINGERS UP,

12:31.663 --> 12:35.667
THEN PRESS DOWN WITH
15 HARD, QUICK THRUSTS.

12:35.798 --> 12:37.278
-NEWMIE: KEEP
YOUR ARMS STRAIGHT,

12:37.408 --> 12:38.409
AND OVER WITH YOUR FINGERS.

12:38.540 --> 12:43.066
-ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE,

12:43.197 --> 12:46.635
SIX, SEVEN, EIGHT, NINE,

12:46.766 --> 12:52.641
TEN, ELEVEN, TWELVE,
THIRTEEN, FOURTEEN, FIFTEEN.

12:52.772 --> 12:54.556
NOW TWO VENTILATIONS.

12:59.300 --> 13:01.345
-HEY, MAN! THIS VATO JUST
SPIT IN MY MOUTH, MAN!

13:01.476 --> 13:05.393
[ANGRY RABBLING]

13:05.523 --> 13:06.916
-GET OFF ME, MAN!

13:07.047 --> 13:08.744
I'M GONNA BUST YOUR
ASS, MAN! COME HERE!

13:09.571 --> 13:11.486
-BEACH BOY.
-GET OFF ME!

13:11.616 --> 13:13.401
-MAN, WHAT'S UP, I'M
GONNA PUNCH YOU OUT.

13:16.578 --> 13:17.709
-HECTOR.

13:19.494 --> 13:21.278
WAIT UP, MAN.
-WHAT DO YOU WANT?

13:22.366 --> 13:23.759
-KICK IT WITH ME
FOR A LITTLE BIT.

13:23.890 --> 13:25.674
-I DID WHAT I HAD TO DO
AND I'M OUT OF HERE.

13:25.805 --> 13:27.241
-HEY, HECTOR, MAN.

13:27.371 --> 13:29.199
COME AND HAVE DINNER
WITH MY JEFITA AND ME.

13:29.330 --> 13:31.114
SHE'D LOVE TO SEE YOU, MAN.

13:31.245 --> 13:32.899
IT'S LIKE BACK IN
THE DAYS, REMEMBER?

13:33.029 --> 13:34.770
-YEAH, WELL THOSE
DAYS ARE OVER.

13:34.901 --> 13:36.772
YOU MOVED AWAY.
YOU, NOT ME.

13:36.903 --> 13:38.992
SO, DON'T THINK I WANT TO
BE YOUR LONG LOST BROTHER.

13:39.906 --> 13:41.429
-MAN, IF YOU REMEMBERED,
YOU WERE LIKE MY BROTHER.

13:41.559 --> 13:42.909
-YEAH, WELL NOT ANYMORE.

13:43.039 --> 13:44.475
YOU'RE IN MALIBU.

13:44.606 --> 13:46.086
I'M STILL BACK THERE
IN THE BARRIO, HOLMES.

13:46.738 --> 13:48.653
-MAN, WE LIVE IN
A GUESTHOUSE, YO.

13:48.784 --> 13:50.351
-IT DOESN'T MAKE
A DIFFERENCE.

13:50.481 --> 13:51.874
YOU TURNED YOUR BACK ON US.

13:53.658 --> 13:55.138
-MAN, COME AND HAVE
DINNER WITH US, MAN.

13:55.269 --> 13:58.968
-NAH, ESE. I'M GOING
WITH MY HOMEBOY.

13:59.099 --> 14:00.927
-EH, LET'S GO, ESE. VAMANOS.

14:01.057 --> 14:03.364
WATCH OUT WITH THE
PAINT JOB, MAN.

14:06.062 --> 14:07.368
LATER, ESE.

14:16.551 --> 14:17.682
-HI, MOM.

14:17.813 --> 14:19.162
-HI? THAT'S IT?

14:24.689 --> 14:26.256
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

14:26.387 --> 14:27.605
-OH, I'M LOADING SOME
NEW CORPORATE SPREADSHEETS

14:27.736 --> 14:29.129
INTO MRS. RHODES' HARD DRIVE.

14:29.259 --> 14:31.261
