SO THEY COULDN'T GET TO YOU.

15:20.267 --> 15:21.529
-I'LL BE OKAY.

15:21.659 --> 15:22.965
-YOU KNOW, I'VE
SPENT TOO MANY NIGHTS

15:23.096 --> 15:24.575
