24:08.708 --> 24:10.361
-IT'S ALL RIGHT, PULGA!
-SHUT UP!

24:10.492 --> 24:12.276
-LET ME TALK TO THEM.
-NO!

24:14.844 --> 24:17.151
-I'LL BE BACK.
