-I WILL.

25:58.644 --> 26:01.647
-HEY, MITCH, HOW'S IT GOING?
-HEY.

26:01.777 --> 26:03.692
-SO WHAT'S NEW?
-AH, NOTHING MUCH.

26:03.823 --> 26:05.607
LET'S SEE, HOBIE'S COMING
INTO TOWN TOMORROW.

26:05.738 --> 26:08.044
IT'S HIS BIRTHDAY.
I GOT HIM A CAR.

26:08.175 --> 26:09.785
-A CAR? ALRIGHT, WHAT KIND?

26:09.916 --> 26:11.700
-I DON'T KNOW YET, SAM'S
TAKING ME TO A POLICE AUCTION.

26:12.396 --> 26:14.442
-YOU AND SAM BEEN SEEING A
LOT OF EACH OTHER LATELY, HUH?

26:14.573 --> 26:15.574
-NOT REALLY.

26:16.749 --> 26:18.141
-ANYTHING GOING
ON BETWEEN YOU TWO?

26:18.272 --> 26:21.144
-YEAH, SURE. WE WORK
TOGETHER, WE'RE FRIENDS.

26:24.583 --> 26:26.497
-MITCH, I'VE ALWAYS BEEN
UPFRONT WITH YOU, RIGHT?

26:26.628 --> 26:27.760
-RIGHT.

26:27.890 --> 26:30.197
-SO, YOU CAN BE
UPFRONT WITH ME.

26:30.806 --> 26:33.026
