YOU TOGETHER OR NOT?

26:33.809 --> 26:34.854
-DEFINE "TOGETHER."

26:35.855 --> 26:36.899
-ARE YOU IN LOVE?

26:39.859 --> 26:41.208
-I THINK SO.

26:41.904 --> 26:43.558
-NEELY WAS RIGHT.
-NO SHE'S NOT RIGHT.

26:43.689 --> 26:44.951
I MEAN, I DON'T
KNOW IF SHE'S RIGHT.

26:45.081 --> 26:47.388
LOOK, MAYBE SHE IS,
MAYBE SHE'S NOT,

26:47.518 --> 26:49.259
BUT WE'RE NOT EVEN SURE YET.

26:49.390 --> 26:51.305
-WHAT HAPPENED?
I MEAN, HOW'D YOU TWO...?

26:52.088 --> 26:55.657
-WELL, THE WHOLE THING
STARTED A COUPLE OF WEEKS AGO

26:55.788 --> 26:57.224
ON A STRAND IN VENICE.

26:58.617 --> 27:00.923
THERE WERE REPORTS OF
PICKPOCKETING AND SOME MUGGINGS.

27:01.054 --> 27:03.926
WE SAW SOME GUY GRAB A LADY'S
PURSE AND TAKE OFF RUNNING,

27:04.057 --> 27:07.756
SO I TOOK OFF AFTER HIM,
SAM WAS RIGHT BEHIND ME.

27:09.628 --> 27:11.630
HE HEADED TOWARD ALL
THE FORTUNE TELLERS

27:11.760 --> 27:12.979
NEAR THE PAVILION.

27:13.109 --> 27:14.415
I CAUGHT UP WITH HIM FIRST.

27:14.545 --> 27:18.811
HE SWUNG THE PURSE
AT ME, I HIT HIM,

27:18.941 --> 27:22.205
AND THEN SAM TACKLED US
BOTH LIKE A LINEBACKER.

27:22.336 --> 27:25.644
WE ALL WENT FLYING INTO
A TABLE WITH TAROT CARDS

27:25.774 --> 27:26.993
AND A CRYSTAL BALL.

27:27.123 --> 27:28.821
THE MUGGER
WAS KNOCKED OUT COLD,

27:28.951 --> 27:32.520
THE CRYSTAL BALL
LANDED ON MY STOMACH.

27:32.651 --> 27:34.870
IT ACTUALLY TOOK MY BREATH AWAY.

27:35.001 --> 27:40.310
WHEN I LOOKED AT SAM, SHE
TOOK MY BREATH AWAY EVEN MORE.

27:40.441 --> 27:43.270
IT WAS WEIRD, I KNEW
SHE FELT IT TOO.

27:43.400 --> 27:45.098
I MEAN, WE BOTH DID.

27:45.228 --> 27:48.188
IT WAS LIKE WE SAW EACH OTHER
FOR THE VERY FIRST TIME.

27:48.754 --> 27:50.320
THE FORTUNE TELLER
PICKED UP A TAROT CARD

27:50.451 --> 27:51.887
THAT LANDED ON SAM.

27:52.018 --> 27:53.497
SHE LOOKED AT THE CARD,
LOOKED AT BOTH OF US,

27:53.628 --> 27:56.065
AND THEN SHE SAID,
"I SEE LOVE FOR YOU BOTH.

27:56.675 --> 27:59.939
"ALL-CONSUMING LOVE,
IT'S IN THE CARDS."

28:02.028 --> 28:05.640
