TURNED OUT TO BE RIGHT.

28:06.467 --> 28:07.860
-YOU UH--

28:07.990 --> 28:10.601
-"ALL-CONSUMING" IS
THE OPERATIVE WORD HERE.

28:10.732 --> 28:12.255
LOOK, THAT WAS
TWO WEEKS AGO.

28:12.386 --> 28:13.779
WE STILL HAVEN'T FIGURED
OUT WHAT'S HAPPENING HERE,

28:13.909 --> 28:14.823
SO WE REALLY DON'T WANT
ANYONE ELSE TO KNOW.

28:14.954 --> 28:15.955
-HEY, I HEAR YOU, MAN.

28:16.085 --> 28:17.260
-ESPECIALLY NEELY.

28:18.000 --> 28:20.046
-I WON'T SAY A WORD,
BUT I DON'T KNOW

28:20.176 --> 28:21.308
